<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/308656-is-this-a-good-read-for-a-book-club">Is this a good read for a book club?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_308656'><a id="like_count_community_question_308656" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/308656?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">12 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17704902-five-days-at-memorial">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/308656-is-this-a-good-read-for-a-book-club">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/308656-is-this-a-good-read-for-a-book-club">See all 6 answers</a>
</li>
